    {
      "step_id": 0,
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "This protocol performs the [96-well Plasmid ezFilter Miniprep Kit](https://www.bioland-sci.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&products_id=137&zenid=6d2c9844db2a12e37e573e104fedbba5). For a detailed list of protocol steps, please see below. Explanation of complex parameters below: * `Number of plates`: Specify whether using 1 (slot 2 alone) or two (slots 2 and 5) plates for this run. * `Number of Samples Plate 1 & 2`: Select the number of samples per plate. If the number of plates variable = 1 above, then the number of samples for plate 2 will be ignored. * `P300 Mount`: Specify which mount (left or right) to host the P300 Multi-Channel Pipette ---",
